Author: icorocket
Title: [ANN][ICO SOON] Galactikka ‚Äì powerfull social network | 50% income for users
Body: Hello, guys. PRE-ICO is finished. We did not get the cap, but received tons of feedback. Also we received feedback from offline meetings and what we are going to do. - Our wp do not describing the product we are aiming to launch. We describe mostly what we have now instead and this was a mistake. Fixing it. - Our marketing budget was 0. And this we will fix too ‚Äî we are seeking early-birds who will invest in us so we can loudly speak about ourselves. - Our website did not reflect the WP. WIP - But conversion was good, as we planned. - We also raising hardcap to 60MM after speaking a lot of business consultants (not from crypto community) - We are hiring new development team. - We are translating existing website and preparing a demo of how the future Galactikka will work.  What is important? We tried to give the world just our project with no promotion. The product - is not enough. And we did a mistake. But it is a common situation for a startup. We are making a pivot.  What next We are moving ICO date to 20 november. Before that we will prepare new WP, website, presentation. While we are doing it ‚Äî follow our chat where we discussing the progress and cryptonews in common.

Author: icorocket
Title: [ANN][ICO SOON] Galactikka ‚Äì powerfull social network | 50% income for users
Body: Hello everyone! Some news. ICO Our PRE-ICO is over. We've learnt a lot of. We collect 23 ETH of 611. Is it fail? At first look ‚Äî it is so.  But only at first. What we've learned a lot: - we measure the effectiveness of the platforms - also we measure the overall conversion (and it is as good as overall on market ‚Äî 1,6% ‚Äî from view to participation) - we found the effective way to communicate with you, guys. No more slack, telegram one love.  Also we spoke with a lot of people from blockchain community, and make this decision: We will make second pre-ico round. Also we will move our main ICO event. And we rethink our roadmap and product model. So we raising the hardcap to $60 000 000. Funds. Advisers. Clear&clean whitepaper  What does it mean to you if you already bought the tokens? It means that your tokens was the cheapest. Because the price of the next tokens will be raised by x3. Thank you for your believing in us.  Soon you will see new WP and finally understand what we want you to see in Galactikka. Keep in mind 50% to users.  P.S. We really hope that there are more people than bounty hunters here (no offense on bounty hunters. As you remember we will giveaway 2 Shiny iPhone X among the participators and referral guys and girls)  If you believe in Galactikka ‚Äî THANK YOU! If you hate Galactikka ‚Äî THANK YOU!. Post down here all your doubts and we will tear them down :-) If you in doubts, what to do? ‚Äî join our Telegram chat
